sp-error-visualizer installation instructions
====================================

1. Compiling from sources
-------------------------

1.1 Dependencies
----------------

The following packages must be installed before sp-error-visualizer:
  libdbus-glib-1-dev(0.88), pkg-config(0.25)

1.2 Compilation & Installation
------------------------------

To compile sp-error-visualizer extract the source archive and do the following
steps in the sp-error-visualizer directory:

  1) Build the sp-error-visualizer binaries with "make"
  2) Install the bult binaries with "make install"
  

1.3 Maemo6 specific configuration
---------------------------------

To enable Maemo6 specific notification system export cflags=-DMAEMO6 
before compiling the sources.